38:40.000 --> 38:43.000
Partly because that's the last novel that Dostoevsky wrote.

38:43.000 --> 38:47.000
I think it's certainly one of the greatest novels of the 19th century.

38:47.000 --> 38:48.000
Maybe the best.

38:48.000 --> 38:50.000
