01:27:07.000 --> 01:27:09.000
That seems a fact.

01:27:09.000 --> 01:27:17.000
It's a fact about Sartre too, though it was harder for him to notice it because he was formed into his privilege.

01:27:17.000 --> 01:27:22.000
But the world reminds us of our thrownness for some more than others.

01:27:22.000 --> 01:27:23.000
Yes, absolutely.

