02:47:37.000 --> 02:47:45.000
The goal is to point out that in the supreme danger lies the saving power.

02:47:45.000 --> 02:47:54.000
The point is to get in the right relation to that understanding of what we are. That allows us to find the joy in it.

02:47:54.000 --> 02:48:00.000
And I think that's a hard thing to do. It's hard to understand even what we're supposed to be doing when we do it.

