Maybe I'm more than you. I'm not of the right generation to be able to do that. But I do think that's got to be the move.

02:48:07.000 --> 02:48:15.000
The move is not to resist it. It's not a nostalgic move. It's an attempt to push people to get in the relation to it.

02:48:15.000 --> 02:48:24.000
That's not the relation of it controlling you and depriving you of stuff. But if you're recognizing some great joy that can be found in it.

02:48:24.000 --> 02:48:33.000
